	<p class="tab2">  <h3>services</h3> </p>
	<p> <b>repair</b>: guitar pedals, synths, amps - if it makes sound I can at least take a look at it. Fee: depends on the job - on average $25-$30 for simple fixes, $50-$100 for more elaborate things. Email for a quote, we can probably work something out. Discounts for b/i/poc. <br><br>
	<b>computer services</b>- I can help you sort out problems with your computer - viruses, slow performance, how to do x or y. Fee: $25-$50 depending on what needs to be done. <br><br>
	<b>art and technology consultancy</b> - Need to integrate arduinos, raspberry pis, and DIY electronic circuits into your art project or installation? I can help you develop tech solutions and debug problems. $40/hr.<br><br>

	
